data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. One or more photo(s) was virtually staged. MOTIVATED SELLER. ASSUMABLE VA LOAN AT 4.75%!!! (Buyer must qualify for VA mortgage product in order to assume for this property). This gorgeous home in Creek Preserve features 3 bedrooms, 2 baths and a  2 car garage.  Built just a year and a half ago, this home showcases modern construction and design elements that meet the demands of contemporary living.  The open floor plan seamlessly integrates the living, dining and living areas, creating a harmonious space for both entertaining guests and everyday relaxation. The open-space kitchen beckons with contemporary mocha cabinets, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances. Washer and dryer also included! Enjoy your evening in a fenced in backyard. The community offers a clubhouse and swimming pool.  Make your appointment today.  Buyers to verify all room dimensions.
